{"tid":1183454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"Google服務嚴重擠塞受阻　美國東岸成重災區","createTime":"2019-06-03T02:31:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-03T05:01:17.000Z","uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"05a4223410dc452007ee2f4cc97ddf6bed83d2fd","tid":1183454,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T02:31:58.000Z","msg":"Google服務嚴重擠塞受阻　美國東岸成重災區<br />\n<br />\nGoogle旗下多項服務包括YouTube、Gmail、Snapchat等周日（6月2日）出現無法連接情況，受影響的地區包括美國、英國、德國和波蘭等地，當中美國東岸的情況最為嚴重。<br />\n事件由美國東岸時間周日下午3時25分開始發生，不少網民到追蹤社交網站故障的獨立網站Down Detector 吐苦水，指無論Gmail、YouTube、Google Drive及Google搜尋器都無法使用。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle的狀態顯示板顯示，該公司旗下超過一半產品都出現異常，只有Google+及 Google Cloud Search正常運作。<br />\n<br />\nGoogle指美國東岸的網絡流量出現大擠塞，導致Google Cloud、GSuite及YouTube等服務受到影響，導致出現遲緩或間歇錯誤的情況。該公司已經發現導致大擠塞的原因，並預計服務會盡快回復正常。<br />\n<br />\nSource: 支01"},{"pid":"5b54cb4d1f8ebff44c89a4b34c03cb9e9b6d3499","tid":1183454,"uid":44358,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T02:35:16.000Z","msg":"Chi Na 大報復<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5b183b2671dde68286eaf7b676859fa47934ef8","tid":1183454,"uid":136186,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T02:36:50.000Z","msg":"中國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"932ac8f0b6cc7bb5c5f38a34bd015402448b69f4","tid":1183454,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T02:37:31.000Z","msg":"又會咁啱64前一兩日壞"},{"pid":"3ddf9a6ed45c6335618daf96e83c45f28d90c385","tid":1183454,"uid":74778,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T02:40:43.000Z","msg":"已發現原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快d講黎聽下關邊個國家事得唔得"},{"pid":"51ebd770857403048fb50a7e9962765e7a478265","tid":1183454,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T02:44:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/mLof_HomF7c/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-t